"{\"uid\": \"rappler.com-sports-rowing-joanie-delgaco-2024-paris-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  SUMMARY  This is AI generated summarization, which may have errors.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 69, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 19, \"end\": 21, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 0.9999973457123571, \"rank\": 2.6542837068614707e-06, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For context, always refer to the full article.\", \"from\": 70, \"to\": 116, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For almost the entirety of her teenage years, Joanie Delgaco was hungry for a volleyball break.\", \"from\": 118, \"to\": 213, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 164, \"end\": 170, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joanie_Cunningham\", \"score\": 0.9624930289605252, \"rank\": 0.03896856383450669, \"text\": \"Joanie\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joanie_Cunningham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joanie_Cunningham\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Standing at 5-foot-5 when she was 17 years old, Delgaco was not exactly tall enough for the sport.\", \"from\": 215, \"to\": 313, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But she stood out as a setter for Camarines Sur in the Palarong Pambansa, attracting volleyball scouts, including one, she said, from NCAA's University of Perpetual Help.\", \"from\": 314, \"to\": 484, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 348, \"end\": 361, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Camarines_Sur\", \"score\": 0.999999991754521, \"rank\": 8.24569770319608e-09, \"text\": \"Camarines Sur\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Camarines_Sur\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Camarines_Sur\"}, {\"begin\": 448, \"end\": 452, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Collegiate_Athletic_Association\", \"score\": 0.9998896618931151, \"rank\": 9.957114205788016e-05, \"text\": \"NCAA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Collegiate_Athletic_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Collegiate_Athletic_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite receiving interest, Delgaco, who eventually became thefirst Filipina rowerto qualify in the country's100-year historyin the Olympics, felt her chance to shine in volleyball was slim.\", \"from\": 486, \"to\": 676, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 554, \"end\": 562, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Filipinos\", \"score\": 0.9171481179897879, \"rank\": 0.0903364248205323, \"text\": \"Filipina\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Filipinos\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Filipinos\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In volleyball back then, I could not see myself excelling [long-term],\\\" Delgaco said in Filipino.\", \"from\": 678, \"to\": 776, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"From age 11 to 17, Delgaco had a volleyball career in sight, even idolizing former UAAP star Alyssa Valdez.\", \"from\": 778, \"to\": 885, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 871, \"end\": 877, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alyssa_Anderson\", \"score\": 0.9999999958877197, \"rank\": 3.616489586652383e-09, \"text\": \"Alyssa\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alyssa_Anderson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alyssa_Anderson\"}, {\"begin\": 878, \"end\": 884, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Framber_Valdez\", \"score\": 0.9216031002264942, \"rank\": 0.08506578929649662, \"text\": \"Valdez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Framber_Valdez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Framber_Valdez\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But eventually, the Iriga native gave herself a reality check.\", \"from\": 886, \"to\": 948, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 906, \"end\": 911, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iriga\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.5850204968656855e-22, \"text\": \"Iriga\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iriga\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iriga\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She felt the need to try something new, so when an opportunity to try out and train for a different sport in Manila came, a teenaged Delgaco took a leap of faith.\", \"from\": 950, \"to\": 1112, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1059, \"end\": 1065, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Metro_Manila\", \"score\": 0.8801492919596358, \"rank\": 0.13617088502515218, \"text\": \"Manila\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Metro_Manila\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Metro_Manila\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Convinced by a rowing coach, Delgaco jumped into her new sport, betting on her physical tools and innate strength, which her mentors believed to be her biggest asset.\", \"from\": 1114, \"to\": 1280, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He really talked to me and my parents.\", \"from\": 1282, \"to\": 1321, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I said alright, if I could do well in rowing, maybe this is really for me,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1322, \"to\": 1407, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Starting without any knowledge of the sport, Delgaco traveled to Manila for the first time in her life.\", \"from\": 1409, \"to\": 1512, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1474, \"end\": 1480, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Metro_Manila\", \"score\": 0.8801492919596358, \"rank\": 0.13617088502515218, \"text\": \"Manila\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Metro_Manila\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Metro_Manila\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She did not even bring a travel bag with her, using instead a cardboard box to pack her clothes and relocate to the city.\", \"from\": 1513, \"to\": 1634, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Slowly, she grasped the fundamentals of rowing, building herself up to go for an Olympic standard 2,000-meter race.\", \"from\": 1636, \"to\": 1751, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Rowing techniques included sculling backward, requiring leg and arm strength in pulling back the paddle - a stark contrast to\\u00a0 dragon boat, which propels the boat forward.\", \"from\": 1753, \"to\": 1924, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"From orchestrating plays for her volleyball team, Delgaco aced captaining her racing shell, the term used for competitive rowing boats.\", \"from\": 1926, \"to\": 2061, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When I started rowing, in under one year, I already won a medal,\\\" shared Delgaco.\", \"from\": 2063, \"to\": 2145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That's when I felt like this is where I am going to excel.\", \"from\": 2146, \"to\": 2205, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And then, every year after that, the blessings did not stop.\\\"\", \"from\": 2206, \"to\": 2267, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"By 2024, her biggest blessing came.\", \"from\": 2269, \"to\": 2304, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Delgaco booked a ticket to the Paris Olympics after placing fourth in the women's single sculls in the World Rowing Asian and Oceanian Qualification Regatta in Chungju, South Korea, last April 21.\", \"from\": 2305, \"to\": 2501, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2408, \"end\": 2420, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Rowing_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"World Rowing\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Rowing_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Rowing_Federation\"}, {\"begin\": 2421, \"end\": 2426, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999999936335, \"rank\": 6.427534544507309e-12, \"text\": \"Asian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 2465, \"end\": 2472, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chungju\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2093732954744546e-19, \"text\": \"Chungju\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chungju\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chungju\"}, {\"begin\": 2474, \"end\": 2485, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"score\": 0.9996862226409672, \"rank\": 0.0003138588027896873, \"text\": \"South Korea\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The feat made her only the fourth rower - and just the first female - in Philippine history to advance to the Olympic games after Edgardo Maerina (1988 Seoul Games), Benjamin Tolentino Jr. (2000 Sydney Games), and Cris Nievarez (2022 Tokyo Games).\", \"from\": 2503, \"to\": 2750, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2669, \"end\": 2687, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benjamin_Tolentino\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Benjamin Tolentino\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benjamin_Tolentino\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benjamin_Tolentino\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Isang malaking karangalan na makapasok sa Olympics lalo na sa sport namin na hindi talaga masyado alam(It is a big honor to advance to the Olympics, especially in a sport that many may not be familiar with),\\\" Delgaco said.\", \"from\": 2752, \"to\": 2975, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It took the 26-year-old three tries, though, noting she tasted defeat in her two previous Olympic attempts.\", \"from\": 2977, \"to\": 3084, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2016, when she was only 18 years old, Delgaco lost her bid for an Olympic ticket, then fell short again in 2021 where she finished just a second shy of qualifying.\", \"from\": 3086, \"to\": 3252, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Part of her up-and-down journey in the sport also saw her snagging the 2019 Southeast Asian Games gold in Manila, and then bowing out in last year's Asian Games in Hangzhou, China.\", \"from\": 3254, \"to\": 3434, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3360, \"end\": 3366, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Metro_Manila\", \"score\": 0.8801492919596358, \"rank\": 0.13617088502515218, \"text\": \"Manila\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Metro_Manila\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Metro_Manila\"}, {\"begin\": 3418, \"end\": 3426, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hangzhou\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.942648682898116e-14, \"text\": \"Hangzhou\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hangzhou\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hangzhou\"}, {\"begin\": 3428, \"end\": 3433, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.5568438310255347, \"rank\": 0.7813571505286877, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But whichever way her campaigns end up, Delgaco always makes sure to represent the country well.\", \"from\": 3436, \"to\": 3532, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"More so now that she's in the sport's biggest stage.\", \"from\": 3533, \"to\": 3585, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Bihira lang mga atletang nakakapasok dito sa Olympic competition(It's rare to be a part of this),\\\" said Delgaco.- Rappler.com  How does this make you feel?\", \"from\": 3587, \"to\": 3743, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3702, \"end\": 3713, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rappler\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rappler.com\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rappler\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rappler\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"follow us\", \"from\": 3745, \"to\": 3754, \"entities\": []}]}"